OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGrey and cloudy with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain through the morning,
OL,7,Fmore isolated during the afternoon.
OL,8,FCloud beginning to break up into the
OL,9,Fevening, with some brighter spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. One or two blustery
OL,11,Fshowers possible. Winds remain
OL,12,Fblustery throughout.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEvening showers ease away
OL,15,Finto the night, with a few late bright
OL,16,Fspells in places. Cloudy skies
OL,17,Fovernight, although any clear spells
OL,18,Fcould lead to a chilly feel in spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
