OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy through the morning
OL,6,Fwith patchy light rain at times. Drier
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon, with some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells. Winds strengthening
OL,9,Flater, fresh inland and strong along
OL,10,Fthe coast overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,13,Fwinds easing Sunday morning, followed
OL,14,Fby the odd blustery shower from the
OL,15,Fwest. Sunshine and light winds Monday;
OL,16,Fbreezier Tuesday but staying dry and
OL,17,Fsunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
